Modifications from the original Code - OSS include:
- Removal of Microsoft proprietary telemetry endpoints and 1DS AppInsights integration
- Removal of Microsoft Treatment Assignment Service (A/B testing)
- Replacement of Visual Studio Marketplace with Open VSX Registry
- Replacement of all Microsoft branding with Son of Anton branding
- Removal of references to Microsoft service endpoints
- Disabling of crash reporting to Microsoft servers

